+ *  (OpenBSD/NetBSD MachFPInterrupt). GXemul instead computed a wrong value
+ *  (float_emul.c always adds the implicit 1-bit, misreading denormal operands,
+ *  and flushes denormal results to +/-0: "FP_SUBNORMAL: TODO").
